[SkillPath "partnership_bidding/basic_notrump"]
[Student "S"]
{WEST has a minimum 1NT opening hand - balanced distribution with 15 points.

EAST has 9 points, which is not enough to bid game, but is worth making an invitational bid. 
So she says 2NT.

Since WEST is minimum he declines the invitation by passing.}

